Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九在這裡做什麽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 正準備回去卻下起了雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 我在等電車重新啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 就讓我們一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位乘客非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.89,0:00:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據剛剛為止的降雪情況
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.02,0:00:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餘下的電車已終止發車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉給您帶來了莫大的麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷腦筋了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是螢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我有很多想説的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但為什麽…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…那個 螢…螢之前在做什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有點事 所以我正準備坐電車過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我意思是你走後做什麽去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 做了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給家族的事業幫忙等等 還挺忙的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九也是 我不在的期間也做了不少事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請務必給我講講
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了神社和公交車站
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.63,0:01:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還去了别的地方 但是到處都空無一人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至想難道說一開始就沒有螢這個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.97,0:01:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫名其妙胡思亂想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麽你什麽都沒說就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢不在的時間 我也做了很多事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店的處境變糟糕過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人手也增加過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:01:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎樣還是順利過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:02.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛開始覺得"算了 現在的狀况還算挺開心"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才發現自己連自己的夢想都已忘卻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便很著急
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天給審查會看了自己的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次認真的給别人看自己的漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺已經…就這樣算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可惡 為什麽要談到這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這明擺著就是亂發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想在重逢時讓你看到一個改變了的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.27,0:02:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明時隔這麽久又見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於這樣的九 我有個東西想給你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這説話方式 又是粗點心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的名字叫超級馬力歐漫畫口香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 果然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超…超級馬力歐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到不僅能吃到囗香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能看一話馬力歐的漫畫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一共十話 而且其中有一話是單行本未收録的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的變成漫畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是組裝式的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以很像拼裝塑料模型的感覺 讓人感覺很興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順帶一提
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那個超恐怖故事的囗香糖一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是頂級廠商掣作出來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣是不是有種"原來如此"的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實"原來如此"得不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我馬上止住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九你能隨意止住眼淚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 總覺得各種感情一下子涌上來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼淚止不住得就落下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九有了認真思考自己喜愛的事物的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 該不該放棄輪不到我來插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九你實際嘗試之後得出的結論才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 看現在的九君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是一臉打算放棄的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能只是想先消沉一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這肯定也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九 抱歉突然就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 那麽再來一次 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡…歡迎回… 這麽説
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 話説回來還真冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 箱子裡的確塞了那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九你也要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小猪拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麽回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這塞滿小猪拉麵的行李箱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都沒帶其他行李嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 那就去把外面的雪放進水壺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.45,0:05:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燒開了來泡小猪拉麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正首班車之前都回不~去~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然還有很多想説和想問的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就逭樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經旱上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢…小…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 你這是在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:07:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 不 該怎麽説好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個 九 電車恢復運行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽 我們回鹿田粗點心店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧 電車停運了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 抱歉讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 今天過來一看你還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機也打不通 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電池沒電了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一小姐 我毫無懸念地落選了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得大家都來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一次落選而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼好失落的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 還有下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是螢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.73,0:08:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽可能還會有像我一樣的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那種確認方法是什麽鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九店長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熟人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才叫了店長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:37.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是臨時店長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽我說 螢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然沒有看錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是臨時的這也是必然的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法違抗的 命中注定的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時機成熟了九
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽 在說什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長 真是不容小覷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九是不可能放到一邊的 被小噍的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重點在這
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 九
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的時候你寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的公司裡比起洋叔更需要九
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起洋叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢的公司？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我準備創辦一家自已的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了實現自已的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以需要九的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸 什麽時候回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那個 比起洋叔 這個時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽 什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年輕人大白天的在粗點心店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:05.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 哥哥是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字叫枝垂紅豐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本是枝垂公司的繼承人的我的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你會到這鎮上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 這段時間在幹什腐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有問候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有名字奇怪的男人在店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一感覺有很多可乘之機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九好像就要被螢搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我不會把九交給任何人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 洋叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能當沒聽過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九是我店裡打工領班的候選人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九是鹿田點心店的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 椰子還有漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫畫的話這有多到賣不完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長不在的話 這個店要怎麽辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我追隨螢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.95,0:11:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這有多到賣不完的粗點心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工領班
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 九
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為 為什麽我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差得遠呢 九
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要緊跟著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再繼續替我拿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:12:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了無論何時都能回到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 螢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要挑戰什麽粗點心呢
